FBIS4-36826 "drnes114_n_94008" FBIS-NES-94-114 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 LEBANON Al-Hirawi Receives Yemeni Justice Minister Al-Hirawi Receives Yemeni Justice Minister NC1306175094 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 13 Jun 94 NC1306175094 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] President Ilyas al-Hirawi received Yemeni Justice Minister 'Abdallah Ahmad Ghanim at the B'abda Palace this evening. Yemeni Ambassador to Lebanon Ahmad Muhammad al-Mutawakkil also attended. After the meeting, the Yemeni minister said that he delivered a verbal message to President al-Hirawi from Yemeni President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih regarding the latest developments of the war in Yemen. He said the war was ignited by the separatists to break up Yemen and to move the country backward. He added: I was pleased by his excellency the president's response and eagerness for Yemen's stability, security, and continued unity. The Yemeni minister arrived in Beirut earlier today.
